SENATE BILL No. 191
_____
DIGEST OF INTRODUCED BILL
Citations Affected: IC 32-21-2.5-8.
Synopsis: Electronic record of confidential address. Exempts a county
recorder from the requirement of accepting an electronic document for
recording if the electronic document contains identifying information
of a person in the address confidentiality program.
Effective: July 1, 2026.
Carrasco
January 5, 2026, read first time and referred to Committee on Judiciary.
